  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive placeable decal, to add flair and decoration to bases.<br><br>This decal commemorates completion of the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Adrift</span> expedition, and to finding peace in a lonely universe.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的可放置贴花，为你的基地增添风格和美观。<br><br>此贴花纪念<span class=\"name name-stellar\">漂泊</span>远征的完成，以及在一个孤寂宇宙中寻得的内心的平静。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的可放置轉印貼紙，可以裝飾基地，增添個人風格。<br><br>這張轉印貼紙是用來紀念完成了<span class=\"name name-stellar\">漂泊</span>探險，在孤獨的宇宙中找到了安寧。"
